⊗ mgks::genesis "risk_assessment"
∴ Schema for Devil's Advocate counterfactual/risk entries

◈ template risk_assessment {
    required:  risk_label      ⟨str⟩
    required:  severity        ⟨f32: 0.0..1.0⟩
    required:  confidence      ⟨f32: 0.0..1.0⟩
    required:  domain          ⟨Strategic | Behavioral | Technical⟩

    optional:  mitigation      ⟨str⟩

    default_tier:    t2
    default_decay:   7d
    default_domain:  Strategic
    agents:          [devils_advocate, conductor]
}
